name: Tough Rack
overview:
Tough Rack provide server racks that power IT systems within small to large organisations.

Different types of server racks are needed for a variety of companies and Tough Rack supply both wall mounted and free standing server rack cabinets. In addition this company doesn’t only supply some of the toughest server cabinets around, but they have engineers who are capable of planning and installing an complete IT infrastructure.

Tough Rack’s Portfolio consists of brands such as Dell, IBM, Cisco, and Citrix. Furthermore, because Tough Rack partner with some of the worlds largest software companies like Adobe and Microsoft they are able to remain independent.
